</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l1">Appeln Fuchs von Dornheım Görgen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l2"><expan>lankwart<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Concʒen klingenuells </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_138_r2l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Appel . Görg vnd Concʒ / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l4">veyntſchaft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Jr ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ludweıg <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Peyern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l5"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> ſune vnd iren <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>leẅte<ex>n</ex></expan> meynt ʒu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l6">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu eẅch 
<add><expan>Hanſ<ex>en</ex></expan></add> Göldlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l7">Dem wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt eẅ <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu reden . Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch . was <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu dıſem mal von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an eẅch werbe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l9">Daʒ Jr Jm das <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l10">etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Paulȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_138" id="68r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Appeln Fuchs von Dornheim, Görgen <expan>Lankwart<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                        Conczen Klingenvells </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Appel, Görg und Concz, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der veyntschaft
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir zu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludweig
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Peyern, <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        sune und iren <expan>lande<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> meynt zu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu ewch
                            <add><expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan></add> Göldlein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch werbe, daz ir im das
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawbet. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Pauli
                            <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
